==Romanian==
===Etymology===
From Late Dacian ''*mellája'' < Dacian ''*melwá-ja'' < [[PIE]] ''*melh1-wo-yo'' ('consisting of flour') < [[PIE]] ''*melh1-wo'' ('flour'). Compare Albanian ''[[miell]]''
===Noun===
'''mălai'''

# [[corn]] [[flour]], [[maize]] [[flour]]
#''(Grains)'' any [[cereal]]
# corn [[flour]] ''(U.S.)'', maize [[flour]] ''(British)''
# [[Romanian]] [[cornbread]]
#''(Plants)'' [[hairy woodrush]] (''Luzula pilosa'')
#''(Plants)'' [[field woodrush]] (''Luzula campestris'')

